Salad Bot Readme
================

This bot is mostly intended for personal use, but feel free to take a gander.

This project uses the discord.py module:
https://discordpy.readthedocs.io/en/stable/index.html


Use/ Enviroment Setup
---------------------

(Add bot token to 'token.txt')

Simple:
    $ pip install -r requirements.txt
    $ python3 bot.py  # or chmod +x bot.py && ./bot.py

Dev/ venv:
    $ python3 -m venv venv
    $ source venv/bin/activate
    $ pip install -r requirements.txt
    $ python bot.py  # or chmod +x bot.py && ./bot.py
